cker </PERSON> was carrying a .357 - caliber Magnum revolver, but did not resist when confronted, the sheriff He was being held in the Mineral County jail on a <LOCATION> California </LOCATION> warrant pending the arrival of <LOCATION> Anaheim </LOCATION> police.
