<HEAD>Education Secretary Visits 30-Pupil High School</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By TOM GARDNER</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>NIXON, Nev. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
