<HEAD>Anti-Arab Anger Sparked by Disappearance of Soldier</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By KARIN LAUB</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>ASHKELON, Israel (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
