<HEAD>Sihanouk Warns Of Khmer Rouge `Blitzkrieg'</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By PETER ENG</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>BANGKOK, Thailand (AP) </DATELINE>
