<HEAD>Protesters March to Denounce Death of Radical Student</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By BARRY RENFREW</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>KWANGJU, South Korea (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
